7. Contingency plans to be prepared for 10 critical facilities including 3 hospitals; 
8. 120 Dam managers and officials of the MoWR to be trained on dam safety and transboundary water negotiations. 
9. 40 inspectors to be trained on chemical and toxic pollution prevention and 1 awareness workshop to be conducted on chemical and toxic pollution.
